    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>HYUNDAI ALLIANCE PLANNED</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Bloomberg News</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>DaimlerChrysler announces formation of alliance with Hyundai Motors; they will cooperate in vehicle production and, perhaps, bid jointly for Daewoo Motors (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>DaimlerChrysler said it was forming an alliance with the Hyundai Motor Company, cementing plans to cooperate in vehicle production and raising the likelihood they would make a joint bid for the Daewoo Motor Company.</p>
      </block>
